dct_title_s: Geologic map of the Arroyo Grande NE quadrangle, San Luis Obispo County, California
dct_description_sm: by Thomas W. Dibblee, Jr. ; edited by John A. Minch.
Relief shown by contours and spot heights.
"Topographic base map from available USGS 7.5-minute quadrangle Arroyo Grande NE, CA 1965, revised 1993, DMA 1854 II NE -- Series V895."
Includes quadrangle location map, index to adjacent 7.5 minute quadrangles, and index to sources of geology.
